These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-1::.
House: modern, tower, cottage, wooden
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, animation, disaster, thriller
1. the tower house is somewhere to the right of the modern house##5
2. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3
3. the person watching comedy movies is in an odd position##4
4. the wooden house is somewhere to the left of the person watching thriller movies##5
5. the person watching comedy movies is the tower house##1
6. the cottage house is the person watching animation movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| House      | wooden  | modern | tower  | cottage |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | thriller      | comedy | animation |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-2::.
City: rome, liverpool, venice, prague
4 different games are played: snooker, domino, go, chess
1. the person traveling to liverpool is between the person playing snooker and the person playing chess##2
2. the person traveling to prague is somewhere to the left of the person playing chess##5
3. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person playing go##1
4. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
5. the person playing domino is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| City   | prague | venice | liverpool   | rome |
| Game           | go      | snooker    | domino | chess      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-3::.
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, rat, hamster, goldfish
City: rome, london, new-york, miami
1. the owner of the rat is the person traveling to london##1
2. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
3. the person traveling to new-york is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to rome##5
4. the person traveling to rome is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
5. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to miami##5
6. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to new-york##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |     3     |   4    |
| Pet        | rat | chinchilla | hamster     | goldfish |
| City   | london  | miami   | new-york | rome    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-4::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, snowboarding, basketball, parkour
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, mechanic, dancer, manager
1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the right of the dancer##5
3. the person who's sport is rowing is between the manager and the mechanic##2
4. the dancer is on the left or right of the manager##3
5. the manager is the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Sport         | basketball | rowing | snowboarding | parkour |
| Job   | manager   | dancer     | mechanic    | lawyer       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, water, juice, milk
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, cain, fonseca, oliveros
1. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the left of the bongani-smoker##5
2. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
3. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the person drinking lemonade##5
4. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
5. the bongani-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
6. the person drinking milk is on the right of the cain-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage          | juice | milk   | lemonade   | water    |
| Cigar   | cain  | oliveros | bongani | fonseca |

