.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, iced-tea, soy-milk, cola
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, tulip, sunflower, orchid
1. the person drinking cola is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking water is somewhere to the left of the person who growsorchid##5
3. the person who growsorchid is between the person drinking cola and the person who growssunflower##2
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |       3        |     4     |
| Beverage           | water | iced-tea | cola | soy-milk |
| Flower   | sunflower        | orchid     | dahlia       | tulip   |

