.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-7::.
City: colone, san-francisco, nizza, edinburgh
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, april, june, november
1. the person who's birthday is in april is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
2. the person traveling to colone is between the person traveling to san-francisco and the person who's birthday is in june##2
3. the person who's birthday is in july is in an even position##4
4. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to colone##5
5. the person traveling to colone is in an even position##4
6. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| City   | san-francisco | colone  | nizza  | edinburgh   |
| Birthday           | november  | july | june | april |

