.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-8::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, trike, roller, subway
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, goldfish, turtle, snake
1. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
2. the person driving the subway is somewhere to the left of the owner of the turtle##5
3. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
4. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
5. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Transport   | trike     | subway | roller     | scooter   |
| Pet    | snake | goldfish  | turtle | guinea-pig |

