.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-9::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, surfing, handball, skateboarding
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, crime, zombie, action
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
4. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere to the right of the person watching action movies##5
5. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching time-travel movies##5
6. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching zombie movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |  4   |
| Sport   | baseball | handball | skateboarding   | surfing |
| Movie-Genre       | time-travel       | zombie   | action | crime |

