.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-10::.
House: cottage, victorian, futuristic, townhouse
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, chef, bartender, journalist
1. the futuristic house is on the left or right of the chef##3
2. the entrepreneur is somewhere to the left of the townhouse house##5
3. the journalist is somewhere to the right of the victorian house##5
4. the entrepreneur is somewhere to the right of the journalist##5
5. the chef is somewhere to the left of the cottage house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |   3    |     4      |
| House   | victorian | futuristic       | cottage   | townhouse        |
| Job      | chef  | journalist | entrepreneur | bartender |

