.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-11::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, november, july, september
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, lavender, azure, lilac
1. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in november##5
2. the person who likes azure is the person who's birthday is in july##1
3. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
4. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the right of the person who likes azure##5
5. the person who likes lavender is somewhere to the left of the person who likes apricot##5
6. the person who likes apricot is on the left or right of the person who likes lavender##3
7. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the right of the person who likes apricot##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4      |
| Birthday   | december | november   | july | september     |
| Color   | lavender     | apricot | azure  | lilac |

