House: tower, gothic-revival, craftsman, futuristic
1. the futuristic house is on the left of the tower house##1
2. the futuristic house is in an even position##4
3. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the left of the gothic-revival house##5
4. the owner of the goldfish is the craftsman house##1
5. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the right of the owner of the lizard##5
6. the gothic-revival house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |  4   |
| Pet   | goldfish | lizard        | frog        | hedgehog |
| House         | craftsman  | futuristic | tower | gothic-revival |

