.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-14::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, december, november, july
There 4 different types of food: banana, watermelon, kale, radish
1. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the right of the person eating kale##5
2. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere to the right of the person eating banana##5
3. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person eating radish##1
4. the person eating radish is the person who's birthday is in november##1
5. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in september##5
6. the person eating watermelon is on the left or right of the person eating banana##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3      |    4     |
| Birthday   | july  | september | december | november |
| Food   | kale | banana | watermelon   | radish  |

