.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-15::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, february, june, october
City: colone, new-york, miami, marseilles
1. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person who's birthday is in february##2
2. the person traveling to colone is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
4. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to miami##5
5. the person traveling to miami is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to marseilles##5
6. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |      3       |     4     |
| Birthday   | march | june  | october      | february |
| City     | miami    | marseilles | new-york | colone   |

