.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-16::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, december, june, october
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, octobercher, fisherman, analyst
1. the person who's birthday is in june is in an even position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the analyst##1
4. the firefighter is in an even position##4
5. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##5
6. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person who's birthday is in february and the octobercher##2
7. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |
| Birthday      | february   | june  | december      | october       |
| Job   | fisherman | analyst | octobercher | firefighter |

