.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, tea, hot-chocolate, sprite
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, dancing, card-games, chess
1. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is chess##5
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
4. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5
5. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Beverage   | fanta     | tea | sprite | hot-chocolate |
| Hobby     | dancing | puzzles    | card-games    | chess |

