.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-18::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, sunflower, poppy, lily
There 4 different types of food: peach, cauliflower, cabbage, carrot
1. the person eating cabbage is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person eating peach is somewhere to the right of the person eating carrot##5
3. the person eating cabbage is somewhere to the left of the person who growstulip##5
4. the person eating peach is somewhere to the left of the person who growssunflower##5
5. the person eating peach is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
6. the person who growstulip is between the person who growslily and the person eating cauliflower##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |       4       |
| Flower      | poppy     | lily | tulip     | sunflower |
| Food   | cabbage | carrot  | peach | cauliflower        |

