.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-20::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, comedy, musical, fantasy
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, zinnia, bellflower, azalea
1. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the person who growszinnia##5
2. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
3. the person who growsbellflower is in an odd position##4
4. the person who growspoppy is somewhere to the right of the person who growszinnia##5
5. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the person who growsazalea##5
6. the person watching zombie movies is between the person watching fantasy movies and the person who growspoppy##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre        | comedy     | fantasy | zombie | musical |
| Flower   | bellflower | azalea | zinnia      | poppy        |

 